  <h2 id="overview">Rental Fleet Overview</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
    <div class="md:w-1/2">
      <p>Dolphin Centrifuge maintains a fleet of Alfa Laval <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/">Decanter Centrifuges</a> for rent, which are suited for:</p>
